profile:
Paving Contractors


WELCOME TO ASPHALT CARE  Since 1985     
Services for Residential Driveways & Parking Lots. 
We repair asphalt all year round including winter

Specializing in Asphalt Repairs, Paving, Driveway Sealing, Pothole Repairs, Catch Basin Repairs, Drainage Issues, Driveway Repairs, Trench Waterproof Patching Along the side of homes, Drain work Patches, Oil Stain Removal, Asphalt Ramps by Garage Entry, Parking Lot Repairs, Asphalt Crack Repairs, Patch Work big and small asphalt repairs.
All our asphalt repairs come with 3 to 5 year guarantee which is the best in the asphalt industry. 

Asphalt Care's name is built on the principles of quality and value. 
We successfully combine our best craftsmanship with new technology and materials. We are constantly striving to exceed the highest industry standards, while creating a look of luxury for your home, or place of business at reasonable prices.

We are property owners and homeowners too, so we know how important it is to have honest reliable contractors working on your home and keeping it clean and safe during and after works been done.  Reputation you can Trust.

We understand your need for honest and straight forward information and want to get the best work for a good price. 
We will work with you side by side and create solutions that meet your budget needs. We believe in higher standards and spend the right amount of time and use only supreme asphalt products. Our attention to detail and patience is what gives us the leading edge. So if your looking for neat quality long lasting asphalt repairs, and asphalt sealing, your at the right place. 

Note to the consumer: Be aware of impostors and scammers. Never give deposits or any money until the job is done. 
If they are sure about there work, then they don't need to worry about there performance.
Also once paving or repairs are done, take a hose and put water over the driveway and make sure that the water is flowing off the driveway and also make sure you don't see standing water.
It will sink and crack your driveway and turn to ice in the winter which can cause tripping more. So when ever you hire a paving contractor, before pay in full, get your water hose and test it.


RESIDENTIAL * COMMERCIAL * RETAIL * Driveways - Parking Lots - Roadways

profile:
Quality and Pride Since 1956
Positano Paving is a family-owned and operated company that was founded by our father A.J. in Toronto in 1956. In 1985, the company relocated to the Barrie area and has been focused on serving Simcoe County ever since. In that time, we have performed thousands of residential and commercial installations including driveways, parking lots, roadways, walkways, sports courts and much more.

Our longevity is a result of the quality of service we provide, our perseverance amidst a number of come-and-go competitors over the last three decades, and the immense personal pride we take in the work we deliver to the neighbours, friends, and people of our community.
